- Update logic to **hide** or **minimize** Todo-related tool calls when in the [Chat](file:///Users/caishanghong/Shopify/cli-tool/llxprt-code-4/packages/cli/src/ui/types.ts#181-185) tab, as the detailed view is now in the [TodoTab](file:///Users/caishanghong/Shopify/cli-tool/llxprt-code-4/packages/cli/src/ui/components/tabs/TodoTab.tsx#14-31).
- Ensure `showTodoPanel` or similar props allow us to completely suppress the inline panel in MainChat.

