- Ensure the [TodoPanel](file:///Users/caishanghong/Shopify/cli-tool/llxprt-code-4/packages/cli/src/ui/components/TodoPanel.tsx#26-30) is properly centered/padded and doesn't cause layout shifting by using `flexGrow={1}` or high-level height constraints in the [MainContent](file:///Users/caishanghong/Shopify/cli-tool/llxprt-code-4/packages/cli/src/ui/components/MainContent.tsx#109-549) container.

